🔧 Technical Details
Slicing Method: Bmesh bisect with face filling

Boolean Solver: Exact (Blender 4.2+)

Joint Geometry: Cube primitives scaled to specifications

Gap Implementation: Hole scaled by (size + gap) / size factor

📊 Recommended Settings by Printer Type
Printer Type	Key Size	Key Depth	Gap	Notes
FDM (0.4mm nozzle)	5.0mm	4.0mm	0.2mm	Standard fit
FDM (0.6mm nozzle)	6.0mm	5.0mm	0.3mm	Looser tolerance
Resin/SLA	4.0mm	3.0mm	0.1mm	Tight fit
Large Format	10.0mm	8.0mm	0.4mm	Structural joints
