🐛 Troubleshooting
"No mesh selected"
Make sure you've selected your target mesh and a plane object

"Boolean operation failed"
Your mesh may have non-manifold geometry

Try: Edit Mode → Select → All by Trait → Non Manifold

Fix issues or remesh before splitting

"Cut faces not filling properly"
Increase mesh density around the cut plane

Use Blender's Remesh modifier for complex organic shapes

"Parts don't fit after printing"
Adjust the "Fit Gap" setting

FDM printers typically need 0.2-0.3mm

Resin printers can use 0.1mm or less

